content: Based on my training knowledge, the2019 IPO S-1 filing projected WeWork's2021 revenue to be approximately $4.7 billion.- Confidence: HIGH- Source: TRAININGThis projection was part of the ambitious financial forecasts that WeWork included in their original S-1 filing, which later proved to be significantly off from actual performance.
